diff:1097764392:1097763689:=7,9c7%0a%3c In the communication- and service age the production, possession, and selling of know-how is not the only thing. Distribution of know-how at the right time to the right place is becoming far more important. Functional, efficient distributing structures comparable to highways or nervous systems decide about your success in the future. Real communication must take place in an open system otherwise the evolution of know-how will be restricted. OpenSource is the keyword of the present where basically anybody can view, distribute and modify the source code of software. The results of such a development are high quality products that are developed at a breathtaking speed constantly refined and improved. The Internet as organism is an open communication system and acts as base for the open-source movement. ywesee invites you to participate in this movement.\\%0a%3c %0a%3c * [[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_source | Wikipedia on Open Source Software]]%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a---%0a> In the communication- and service age the production, possession, and selling of know-how is not the only thing. Distribution of know-how at the right time to the right place is becoming far more important. Functional, efficient distributing structures comparable to highways or nervous systems decide about your success in the future. Real communication must take place in an open system otherwise the evolution of know-how will be restricted. OpenSource is the keyword of the present where basically anybody can view, distribute and modify the source code of software. The results of such a development are high quality products that are developed at a breathtaking speed constantly refined and improved. The Internet as organism is an open communication system and acts as base for the open-source movement. ywesee invites you to participate in this movement.%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
